message.entry: Vals must have same number of rows as XYCoordinates.
Matrix size must be equal to grid size.
Calling move on individual map layers is not supported when they are contained within a multiLayerMap..
GPU Arrays are not supported during code generation.
GetTransformFcn must preserve the size of outputs retrieved from the mapLayer during getMapData.
SetTransformFcn must preserve the size of inputs provided to the mapLayer during setMapData.
Size vector must have finite upper bound.
